{"type":"click","text":"OUTSHINE — Grains\n        \n          \n          \n            Drop Zone\n            Browse Files\n            Recent Grains\n          \n          \n          \n            \n              🦪\n              The shell is open. Drop grains here.\n              WAV files, folders, or XPN archives\n            \n          \n          \n          \n            Grains:\n            Rhodes_C3 ×\n            Rhodes_C4 ×\n            Rhodes_C5 ×\n            \n            3 grains\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      B — Tabbed with Grain Strip\n      Three tabs: Drop Zone (default), Browse Files, Recent Grains. Selected files accumulate in a bottom strip regardless of which tab you're on. Maximizes space for each mode. \"Recent Grains\" remembers your last 20 imports.","choice":"tabbed-split","id":null,"timestamp":1774466071712}
{"type":"click","text":"OUTSHINE — Grains\n        \n          \n          \n            Drop Zone\n            Browse Files\n            Recent Grains\n          \n          \n          \n            \n              🦪\n              The shell is open. Drop grains here.\n              WAV files, folders, or XPN archives\n            \n          \n          \n          \n            Grains:\n            Rhodes_C3 ×\n            Rhodes_C4 ×\n            Rhodes_C5 ×\n            \n            3 grains\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      B — Tabbed with Grain Strip\n      Three tabs: Drop Zone (default), Browse Files, Recent Grains. Selected files accumulate in a bottom strip regardless of which tab you're on. Maximizes space for each mode. \"Recent Grains\" remembers your last 20 imports.","choice":"tabbed-split","id":null,"timestamp":1774466072659}
{"type":"click","text":"OUTSHINE — Grains\n        \n          \n          \n            DROP ZONE\n            \n              🦪\n              Drop grains here\n              WAV • Folders • XPN\n            \n            Drag from Finder, MPC software, or any DAW\n          \n          \n          \n            BROWSE\n            \n              ← Back\n              ~/Music/Samples/Rhodes/\n            \n            \n              \n                📁 Velocity Layers/\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C3.wav 2.4s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C4.wav 2.1s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C5.wav 1.8s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_DI_raw.wav 8.2s\n              \n              \n                📁 Round Robins/\n              \n            \n            \n              Select All WAVs\n              Add Selected →\n            \n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A — Vertical Split\n      Drop zone left, folder browser right. Equal weight. Both always visible. The browser has navigation (back, path bar) and file selection with \"Add Selected\" to move files into the pipeline.","choice":"vertical-split","id":null,"timestamp":1774466221829}
{"type":"click","text":"OUTSHINE — Grains\n        \n          \n          \n            DROP ZONE\n            \n              🦪\n              Drop grains here\n              WAV • Folders • XPN\n            \n            Drag from Finder, MPC software, or any DAW\n          \n          \n          \n            BROWSE\n            \n              ← Back\n              ~/Music/Samples/Rhodes/\n            \n            \n              \n                📁 Velocity Layers/\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C3.wav 2.4s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C4.wav 2.1s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C5.wav 1.8s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_DI_raw.wav 8.2s\n              \n              \n                📁 Round Robins/\n              \n            \n            \n              Select All WAVs\n              Add Selected →\n            \n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A — Vertical Split\n      Drop zone left, folder browser right. Equal weight. Both always visible. The browser has navigation (back, path bar) and file selection with \"Add Selected\" to move files into the pipeline.","choice":"vertical-split","id":null,"timestamp":1774466224044}
{"type":"click","text":"OUTSHINE — Grains\n        \n          \n          \n            DROP ZONE\n            \n              🦪\n              Drop grains here\n              WAV • Folders • XPN\n            \n            Drag from Finder, MPC software, or any DAW\n          \n          \n          \n            BROWSE\n            \n              ← Back\n              ~/Music/Samples/Rhodes/\n            \n            \n              \n                📁 Velocity Layers/\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C3.wav 2.4s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C4.wav 2.1s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_C5.wav 1.8s\n              \n              \n                🎵 Rhodes_DI_raw.wav 8.2s\n              \n              \n                📁 Round Robins/\n              \n            \n            \n              Select All WAVs\n              Add Selected →\n            \n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A — Vertical Split\n      Drop zone left, folder browser right. Equal weight. Both always visible. The browser has navigation (back, path bar) and file selection with \"Add Selected\" to move files into the pipeline.","choice":"vertical-split","id":null,"timestamp":1774466224944}
